{"lang":"fr","stage":5,"title":"everyday sentences, growing","sentences":[{"t":"Je sais pas où je suis.","en":"I don't know where I am.","a":"n_2e40ed199739.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais pas où c'est.","en":"I don't know where it is.","a":"n_2b7ae9022cc0.mp3"},{"t":"Elle vient d'où ?","en":"Where is she from?","a":"n_cb3472d4e346.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis à la bourre.","en":"I'm running late.","a":"n_f1b8e8681afc.mp3"},{"t":"Ça fait un peu mal.","en":"It hurts a little.","a":"n_280bd5079d26.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai mal nulle part.","en":"Nothing hurts.","a":"n_0ce6b94234fd.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai pas le temps aujourd'hui.","en":"I don't have time today.","a":"n_98e9bc728451.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis pas d'ici.","en":"I'm not from here.","a":"n_bb0231871b57.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais pas quoi faire.","en":"I don't know what to do.","a":"n_9cd010bd1040.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis un peu fatigué.","en":"I'm a little tired.","a":"n_b143118729af.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis vraiment crevé aujourd'hui.","en":"I'm really tired today.","a":"n_c93768abd94d.mp3"},{"t":"J'aime bien ta maison.","en":"I like your house.","a":"n_b089991af52a.mp3"},{"t":"Aujourd'hui je fais rien.","en":"Today I'm doing nothing.","a":"n_0ebae3470415.mp3"},{"t":"Je fais tout tout seul.","en":"I do everything by myself.","a":"n_a71d58a3c101.mp3"},{"t":"Ça se fait pas.","en":"You don't do that.","a":"n_b2d5f74889cd.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux rentrer chez moi.","en":"I want to go home.","a":"n_f141c2937a24.mp3"},{"t":"On est quel jour aujourd'hui ?","en":"What day is it today?","a":"n_ba91dadd71ec.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux acheter un café.","en":"I want to buy a coffee.","a":"n_4b6898b4f354.mp3"},{"t":"Tu veux faire quoi aujourd'hui ?","en":"What do you want to do today?","a":"n_b9b09fc81b44.mp3"},{"t":"On va manger un truc.","en":"Let's go eat something.","a":"n_0fa6652679b9.mp3"},{"t":"C'est pas mon ami.","en":"He's not my friend.","a":"n_72a3f8902a50.mp3"},{"t":"C'est mon ami.","en":"He's my friend.","a":"n_b3f302009add.mp3"},{"t":"Voici mon ami.","en":"This is my friend.","a":"n_375b98ceb56a.mp3"},{"t":"C'est moi qui fais à manger.","en":"I make the food.","a":"n_790cd447dac6.mp3"},{"t":"C'est comment, à manger ?","en":"How's the food?","a":"n_bd03c9a43b8f.mp3"},{"t":"Ça coûte combien tout ça ?","en":"How much is all of this?","a":"n_c1bce1cf4fc9.mp3"},{"t":"Le bus c'est combien ?","en":"How much is the bus?","a":"n_debe7460211e.mp3"},{"t":"Je me sens pas bien.","en":"I don't feel well.","a":"n_0f720bcef6c8.mp3"},{"t":"Je me sens mieux maintenant.","en":"I feel better now.","a":"n_a7c798eccd61.mp3"},{"t":"Et toi, t'es qui ?","en":"And who are you?","a":"n_b85edbed4154.mp3"},{"t":"Le bus est tout près.","en":"The bus is close.","a":"n_9dfbf46afebb.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai peu d'argent aujourd'hui.","en":"I have a little money today.","a":"n_2f1409288485.mp3"},{"t":"Ça fait beaucoup d'argent.","en":"That's a lot of money.","a":"n_56973ab75685.mp3"},{"t":"Y a quoi à manger ?","en":"What is there to eat?","a":"n_024d6fa20071.mp3"},{"t":"Tu y vas ou pas ?","en":"Are you going or not?","a":"n_73d69d18517f.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai rien fait aujourd'hui.","en":"I didn't do anything today.","a":"n_e7b1358c4ab1.mp3"},{"t":"Hier j'ai rien fait.","en":"Yesterday I did nothing.","a":"n_39ddf06c9a2c.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai rien fait hier.","en":"I didn't do anything yesterday.","a":"n_650da78d5db4.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis dans la cuisine.","en":"I'm in the kitchen.","a":"n_bf3375a61e47.mp3"},{"t":"La cuisine est ici.","en":"The kitchen is here.","a":"n_2ca69a2b16b6.mp3"},{"t":"Elle est où, la cuisine ?","en":"Where's the kitchen?","a":"n_71f768236342.mp3"},{"t":"Il est où, le médecin ?","en":"Where's the doctor?","a":"n_9b7107c955da.mp3"},{"t":"Je vais chez le médecin aujourd'hui.","en":"I'm going to the doctor today.","a":"n_3c420763e8c7.mp3"},{"t":"Je dois aller chez le médecin.","en":"I need to go to the doctor.","a":"n_1384c528460f.mp3"},{"t":"Je me sens vraiment mal.","en":"I feel really bad.","a":"n_f340a0960050.mp3"},{"t":"Je voudrais un café.","en":"I'd like a coffee.","a":"n_d3124bc3de30.mp3"},{"t":"Il est où, mon téléphone ?","en":"Where's my phone?","a":"n_d66e7bc311bd.mp3"},{"t":"Je te vois mal.","en":"I can't see you well.","a":"n_3de16fb7f72c.mp3"},{"t":"On se voit plus tard.","en":"I'll see you later.","a":"n_08934b49f94e.mp3"},{"t":"Aujourd'hui je me lève tard.","en":"Today I'm getting up late.","a":"n_5de1e5eb8456.mp3"},{"t":"Demain je me lève tôt.","en":"Tomorrow I'm getting up early.","a":"n_caf95d7acdcf.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais pas quoi commander.","en":"I don't know what to order.","a":"n_21ca7ba930e6.mp3"},{"t":"Tu vas commander quoi ?","en":"What are you going to order?","a":"n_b05b7a434a7b.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai envie de dormir.","en":"I feel like sleeping.","a":"n_f788c5fe6aa2.mp3"},{"t":"T'as envie de sortir ?","en":"Do you feel like going out?","a":"n_d9744c8ceacb.mp3"},{"t":"L'eau c'est combien ?","en":"How much is the water?","a":"n_945c5131d8ff.mp3"},{"t":"On est dans la cuisine.","en":"We're in the kitchen.","a":"n_ba93dc61c68d.mp3"},{"t":"J'aimerais apprendre plus.","en":"I'd like to learn more.","a":"n_590fc5f2b8a1.mp3"},{"t":"Tu devrais pas faire ça.","en":"You shouldn't do that.","a":"n_dc0493fbf017.mp3"},{"t":"Tu devrais pas autant travailler.","en":"You shouldn't work so much.","a":"n_15e240f43a2d.mp3"},{"t":"Pourquoi tu viens pas ?","en":"Why aren't you coming?","a":"n_13548197d698.mp3"},{"t":"Tu viens à quelle heure ?","en":"What time are you coming?","a":"n_7d1d76a98bdf.mp3"},{"t":"C'est près ou loin ?","en":"Is it close or far?","a":"n_3cb5a5da4734.mp3"},{"t":"Le train coûte pas cher.","en":"The train is cheap.","a":"n_512163f4545d.mp3"},{"t":"Le train est loin.","en":"The train is far.","a":"n_96a862609c37.mp3"},{"t":"T'as quelque chose de moins cher ?","en":"Do you have anything cheaper?","a":"n_b44e25c52503.mp3"},{"t":"C'est encore moi.","en":"It's me again.","a":"n_2788c067fdd5.mp3"},{"t":"J'arrive dans cinq minutes.","en":"I'll be there in five minutes.","a":"n_2f2abaf96d0c.mp3"},{"t":"J'aime sortir avec toi.","en":"I like going out with you.","a":"n_a5fe4b2e318f.mp3"},{"t":"J'aimerais y aller avec toi.","en":"I'd like to go with you.","a":"n_db644d09f09d.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux apprendre l'espagnol avec toi.","en":"I want to learn Spanish with you.","a":"n_dca5ca72c532.mp3"},{"t":"Demain je vais étudier.","en":"Tomorrow I'm going to study.","a":"n_924abe261dd1.mp3"},{"t":"Personne m'a rien dit.","en":"Nobody told me anything.","a":"n_e322ec6f92ab.mp3"},{"t":"Il te l'a dit quand ?","en":"When did he tell you?","a":"n_b12ae4d37448.mp3"},{"t":"T'as mal depuis quand ?","en":"How long has it been hurting?","a":"n_1dcb202c1e1c.mp3"},{"t":"Je me couche tôt aujourd'hui.","en":"I'm going to bed early today.","a":"n_343594c8ff46.mp3"},{"t":"Comment je vais en ville ?","en":"How do I get downtown?","a":"n_e17fc95ae827.mp3"},{"t":"Pourquoi t'es triste ?","en":"Why are you sad?","a":"n_f78cfab2abd3.mp3"},{"t":"Il a dit quoi sur moi ?","en":"What did he say about me?","a":"n_ec59a5769fb5.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux la même chose.","en":"I want the same thing.","a":"n_7d86e629af4c.mp3"},{"t":"Je peux poser une question ?","en":"Can I ask a question?","a":"n_ab8ed26515ab.mp3"},{"t":"Il demande toujours la même chose.","en":"He always asks the same thing.","a":"n_f25cae9f1792.mp3"},{"t":"Qui demande après moi ?","en":"Who's asking about me?","a":"n_b96ae7d8110b.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais pas quoi dire.","en":"I don't know what to say.","a":"n_58ad02f294a2.mp3"},{"t":"Aujourd'hui je fais pas de sport.","en":"I'm not working out today.","a":"n_44dccda9078b.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux faire plus de sport.","en":"I want to work out more.","a":"n_8b8f23773e85.mp3"},{"t":"Tu connais mon ami ?","en":"Do you know my friend?","a":"n_cb7db34dcd4e.mp3"},{"t":"Je vais payer maintenant.","en":"I'm going to pay now.","a":"n_183fead32dc9.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux pas payer autant.","en":"I don't want to pay that much.","a":"n_f93c0c821c74.mp3"},{"t":"Le taxi est là.","en":"The taxi is here.","a":"n_7aa53be47b0a.mp3"},{"t":"J'arrive dans dix minutes.","en":"I'll be there in ten minutes.","a":"n_b6307dde52be.mp3"},{"t":"J'arrive à dix heures.","en":"I arrive at ten.","a":"n_1e2e05d25844.mp3"},{"t":"Je m'appelle pas comme ça.","en":"That's not my name.","a":"n_15411d8facaf.mp3"},{"t":"Je vais à la fête.","en":"I'm going to the party.","a":"n_19f854136863.mp3"}]}